node.text: I took this orange $4.99 lamp from Goodwill and gave it a little makeover. The power of paint!!😍

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Chelsea🌿 on August 24, 2021 tagging @target, @bedbathandbeyond, @magnolia, @ohsweetskye, and @boutiquerugs. May be an image of furniture and bedroom.

node.text:
Fresh paint!👩‍🎨 I painted an accent wall in the bedroom yesterday. What do you think?🤔 The color is Flower Jar by @magnolia . It’s a greenish grey color. Beautiful color…maybe add some darker accents? Can’t decide….
.
.
.
